		<div id="content"><span class="title">Welcome to Scrapaholix</span><hr /><p><span style="font-size: medium;"><img height="149" src="http://www.scrapaholix.com/web_media/Image/image1.jpg" style="float: right; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px;" width="300" />Welcome to the official Scrapaholix website. Scrapaholix is a long established kit club that is based around teaching techniques to scrapbookers and papercrafters alike. Each member is provided with a gorgeous kit that is carefully put together every month, with enough stash to make 2-4 layouts. See what we have been up to in the gallery!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><img height="150" src="http://www.scrapaholix.com/web_media/Image/image2.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px;" width="300" />There are clubs all over the UK who will welcome you if you would like to join in the fun! Check out the locations page to see if there is a club near you. Alternatively if there is no club in your area and you would be interested in starting one, please contact me for more information, I would love to hear from you!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">If joining a club is not your thing, why not consider a virtual club? You will be provided with the monthly kit as well as notes relevant to that month's technique. <span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Please contact me for more information.</span></p>
